<emphasis id="B95E0B5E37441B64FF6E4152FEDDE81C" bold="true" box="[192,340,1794,1818]" pageId="7" pageNumber="6">Etymology</emphasis>
. We are pleased to name this species in honor of Marcela Laura Monné, for her friendship and many contributions to the study of Neotropical 
<taxonomicName id="4C2AACCF37441B64FCEF4172FC7CE83C" authorityName="Latreille" authorityYear="1802" box="[833,1013,1826,1850]" class="Insecta" family="Cerambycidae" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="7" pageNumber="6" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="family">Cerambycidae</taxonomicName>
. The epithet is a noun in the genitive case.
</paragraph>
<caption id="DF5587C4374B1B6BFF47417DFAF1E845" box="[233,1400,1837,1859]" pageId="8" pageNumber="7" startId="8.[233,317,1837,1859]" targetBox="[233,1400,192,1821]" targetPageId="8">
